{"tid":417422,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"你班大種乞丐，有冇買車冇錢泊車，泊撚到一街都係車","createTime":"2017-09-28T15:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T02:10:39.000Z","uid":4655,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"08a820f2417cbfaa3299833031229be7274f4c93","tid":417422,"uid":4655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"你買條金魚返屋企都諗下屋企有冇位放啦。<br />\n<br />\n買部車又就咁擺街，阻撚住條路，冇錢養車就搭巴士。<br />\n<br />\n衰撚個乞丐"},{"pid":"894a39da0cbcf5cd541db5c2f63533e008cffd25","tid":417422,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47e8bfa34b403507f414d715ad8dd98d349e1c1","tid":417422,"uid":27766,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T15:56:36.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係冇停車場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29eeb7390d45ae81a03f9085393b3640e8f6d3f","tid":417422,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:02:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇諗過係冇停車場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果邊有兩個，架車幾十到成百粒都仲要泊到塞撚住條路，揸電單車都好難出到去"},{"pid":"f6cc9d9cc795349bc1f6203ad9614ba8045450c1","tid":417422,"uid":4655,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:15:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇諗過係冇停車場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇諗過冇停車場唔代表可以泊街<br />\n<br />\n講真，貨車拖頭搵食車早出晚歸泊埋山邊工廠區，搵食車夜晚泊下街唔阻人真係情有可原。<br />\n<br />\n但係私家車真係冇藉口。好似我住個區，冇錯，附近公屋居屋停車場都爆到七彩，但其實有私人樓有車位放租，係d人嫌貴唔租。<br />\n<br />\nd仆街一係冇錢一係貪方便，過兩條街工廠區有錶位晚晚都有位又唔泊，係都要泊正樓下，僥倖心態冇抄當賺左，抄左當比停車場。<br />\n<br />\n係咪下下都要第一城咁撚樣先可以治到d仆街先？"},{"pid":"b642f10835fbc442ab1a55eddad588cae0703db9","tid":417422,"uid":63247,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:16:46.000Z","msg":"我落車去隔離買d野係咪都要入停車場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6677dfd9484237ed61f02fe2669aa39d2b5d1dbe","tid":417422,"uid":4655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇諗過係冇停車場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果邊有兩個，架車幾十到成百粒都仲要泊到塞撚住條路，揸電單車都好難出到去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一切都係藉口， 一係諗縮數，二係貪方便"},{"pid":"61ea8b40c57b28d27c0421efeb8229617a92b9c5","tid":417422,"uid":52591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:21:57.000Z","msg":"最緊要方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4569887cc51215b07895bf8b1f15083ad00e3c","tid":417422,"uid":4655,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我落車去隔離買d野係咪都要入停車場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係聖人，我都唔係冇試過就咁泊街，但揸住架車，我一係快快手手，一係搵人落車買野，我係車度等。<br />\n<br />\nD仆街去商場老奉泊車老免，一係就R 酒樓飛，一係就買衫呃泊車再退錢。人唔叫狗都吠"},{"pid":"9f297de18227c8aebd0bb329f524a9347010a3a1","tid":417422,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:27:56.000Z","msg":"泊街都算，有d撚樣泊灣位，泊到擋住行人過路位，double park，或者阻住其他車或者行人視線，做同一件事，香港人唔會做到cheap曬既我諗唔到有幾多"},{"pid":"34eab7bb3cecae787d79a7db393e051e9c8a9c98","tid":417422,"uid":4655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T16:31:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泊街都算，有d撚樣泊灣位，泊到擋住行人過路位，double park，或者阻住其他車或者行人視線，做同一件事，香港人唔會做到cheap曬既我諗唔到有幾多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實，你唔影響到人，真係問題不大。香港地方細， 你做小小野都已經有機會影響到人。所以真係有d公德心"},{"pid":"f571098a1881731dfe989d8f7068e660fbd90064","tid":417422,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T22:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我落車去隔離買d野係咪都要入停車場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最撚叻就係駁嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔明樓主講乜就去學下中文啦Ching"},{"pid":"38d9cbf663da5dce4f26acb2f5fac38367ec564f","tid":417422,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T23:03:18.000Z","msg":"作為一位熱心市民有需要就打999<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e45981b4a11a03e38f9238e526308e3a8609ea","tid":417422,"uid":133450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T23:24:54.000Z","msg":"打去當區差館投訴喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43cd4bb2e93010d47b24d744a828db0e27681c1c","tid":417422,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T00:10:35.000Z","msg":"方便係大過一切"},{"pid":"0a996d833ca44f7c711242406d35798216cebdca","tid":417422,"uid":67700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T02:10:39.000Z","msg":"你行緊果條路就屌人泊街阻住<br />\n到你到左要去既地方就貪平貪方便泊街<br />\n個個都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有足夠合理價錢同夠近既停車場有邊個唔想用<br />\n但係個政府偏要拆中環尖沙咀呢啲旺區停車場大樓<br />\n要屌就屌個政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}